<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Invoice - {{auctionTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .invoice-details {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Invoice for Your Sale</h1>
        <p>Congratulations on completing your auction!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Your auction for <strong>{{auctionTitle}}</strong> has been successfully completed!</p>
        
        <div class="invoice-details">
            <h3>Invoice Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{invoiceDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Final Amount:</strong> <span class="amount">${{finalAmount}}</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>A detailed PDF invoice has been attached to this email for your records.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Review the attached invoice</li>
            <li>Contact the buyer to arrange item pickup/delivery</li>
            <li>Complete the transaction through the platform</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Your earnings will be processed according to our platform's payment schedule.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions about your sale or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for using Tap2Win!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Tap2Win Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent from Tap2Win Auction Platform</p>
        <p>Â© 2024 Tap2Win. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
